# Bill Generator

This C program automatically replaces placeholders in a text file with user input, generating a personalized bill.

## Features

- Reads a bill template from `myfile.txt`.
- Replaces placeholders `(name)`, `(item)`, and `(outlet)` with user inputs.
- Saves the personalized bill to `myfile2.txt`.
- Displays the final bill on the screen.

## How to Use

1. Run the program.
2. Enter your **name**, **purchased item**, and **outlet name** when prompted.
3. The program will read the original file and replace the placeholders.
4. View the output in the console and in `myfile2.txt`.
